When I try `gdb ipython` I get:

```
"/Users/me/anaconda/bin/ipython": not in executable format: File format not recognized
```

Apparently the OSX version of strace is dtrace. Results (/meaningless gibberish?) here:
https://gist.github.com/ohadle/5c73237d337f2b955d00c9ec857ab0a8
